minor.comment: Add a `valueDocumentationComment` option to `exportAsDefault` that allows a documentation comment to be generated for the exported value.
Rename the `documentationComment` property in the `exportAsDefault` value to `interfaceDocumentationComment`.

patch.comment: Fix an issue where `inferDefaultExportInterfaceNameFromFilename` did not apply.

minor.comment: Expand the typings generator to take a richer set of options for default exports. See `exportAsDefault` in @rushstack/typings-generator's `StringValuesTypingsGenerator`. Also included is another property in `exportAsDefault`: `inferInterfaceNameFromFilename`.
Update the schema for `.loc.json` files to allow string names that include the `$` character.

patch.comment: Include CHANGELOG.md in published releases again
Include missing `type` modifiers on type-only exports.
Fix line endings in published package.
Update type-only imports to include the type modifier.

minor.comment: Add an option to output typings to additional output folders.
(BREAKING CHANGE) Remove the legacy RESX reader functions.

patch.comment: Allow the package to be webpacked.

minor.comment: Remove the validation of RESX string names.
Refactor the RESX parser to follow a similar API as the other parsers.
Add the ability to ignore strings from loc file parsing.
Expose each parser directly so that they can be used with arbitrary file extensions.
Add the ability to tweak string comments in generated typings.
Include an option to ignore strings from typings generation.
